，赤红的耳颊，唔咽声。我真的不知道打孩子的时候周微妈妈有没有心疼过。周微以后要怎么面对学校里的同学，真的丢脸啊。"},"attached_info":"CkEI8+fpsYLNxIwKEAMaCTExMjY2MTM1MiC0jdO7BjAAOOglQBRyCjg0MjUwMTUyNzl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"41 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-05ff439fd7ab93e7cba661dcb14c67e7_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"21_1735960978.109050","card_id":"Q_622711945","target":{"id":622711945,"title":"为什么港币上印着渣打和汇丰的名字?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/622711945","type":"question","created":1695085738,"answer_count":39,"follower_count":208,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[205,26673],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkAI8+fpsYLNxIwKEAMaCTEwMDY1OTc3OSCq6aOoBjAAONABQBVyCTYyMjcxMTk0NXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"40 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-93e10d9ba2aba34876dccf393d598462_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"22_1735960978.109272","card_id":"Q_423321345","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":423321345,"title":"中国特有的狸花猫有多强大？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/423321345","type":"question","created":1601282522,"answer_count":1635,"follower_count":7381,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1570,95032,176731,290769],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8I8+fpsYLNxIwKEAMaCDU2MzUwMDk3INrDxvsFMAA41TlAFnIJNDIzMzIxMzQ1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"33 万热度",